casebody.data:
No. 913. No. 101,

Misc.

Finley v. Ragen, Warden. Ex parte Finley. February 3, 1947.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the Criminal Court of Cook County, Illinois; and

The petition for writ of certiorari is denied. The motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus is also denied.
